t have good druid drops?<br>
<br>
Why would /anyone/ hunt in a spot that doesn't drop something that they can use?  It just doesn't make sense.  If a T-Staff drops in Karnors, who's to say that the monk 'needs' the T-Staff more than I need the Lodi Shield (and whatever else I may be able to get for it)?  If someone /demands/ an item, JUST because their class can use it, doesn't make them any less greedy than someone who's going to /trade/ that item for something /they/ can use.<br>
